title: 2022 CFB Pick Em Week 9
description:
The boys are back for Week 9. Doogs had a huuuuge mess up when it came to last week's Pick Em Parlay and we get to the bottom of it. Looking forward there's some controversy regarding the Barstool Invitational, specifically the Halftime Show.


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
